{{Quote|Platoon leaders, switch your comlinks to encrypted command frequency zero-zero-four. Have your troopers fan out. Grid search. Every building, every nook and cranny. You know what you're up against, so keep your wits about you.|Commander Salvo to his squad|<ref name="Dark Lord: The Rise of Darth Vader">''[[Dark Lord: The Rise of Darth Vader]]''</ref>}}
'''004''' was an encrypted communication frequency used by the [[Clone trooper/Legends|clone troopers]] of the [[Grand Army of the Republic/Legends|Grand Army of the Republic]], during the final [[Standard year/Legends|years]] of the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]]. This frequency was used when [[Order 66/Legends|Order 66]] was issued, so that the [[Cloning/Legends|clones]] could communicate with each other while searching for any surviving [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] on [[Murkhana/Legends|Murkhana]].

